## 3ï¸âƒ£ Core DevOps Concepts (Must Know)

### ğŸ”¹ CI/CD

* **CI (Continuous Integration):**

  * Developers push code frequently
  * Automated build & tests run
* **CD (Continuous Delivery/Deployment):**

  * Code automatically deployed to staging/production

### ğŸ”¹ Infrastructure as Code (IaC)

* Infrastructure defined using code
* Reproducible & version-controlled
* Tools: **Terraform, CloudFormation**

### ğŸ”¹ Configuration Management

* Maintain server configurations consistently
* Tools: **Ansible, Chef, Puppet**

### ğŸ”¹ Monitoring & Logging

* Detect failures early
* Improve reliability
* Tools: **Prometheus, Grafana, ELK**

